OL,3,CFormer Tory leader warns of
OL,4,Cexistential threat if party fails to
OL,5,Cpull together
OL,7,FThe comments were made to ITV News
OL,8,FDeputy Political Editor Anushka
OL,9,FAsthana as part of the Tonight
OL,10,Fprogramme Rishi Sunak: Up Close
OL,12,FWilliam Hague has called on Tory
OL,13,Frebels to stop the in-fighting, with a
OL,14,Fchilling warning that if the party
OL,15,Fgoes into opposition, it may never
OL,16,Freturn to government.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G1/15
