OL,3,CFormer Tory leader warns of
OL,4,Cexistential threat if party fails to
OL,5,Cpull together
OL,7,FThe former Tory leader said that while
OL,8,Fthings were "difficult, exhausting,
OL,9,Fand exasperating" for Rishi Sunak, he
OL,10,Fwas sure the PM would keep calm in
OL,11,Fresponse.
OL,13,F"This is a very resilient person who
OL,14,Fcan keep going for a long time under
OL,15,Fdifficult conditions, without
OL,16,Fpanicking, without losing heart, and
OL,17,Fwithout losing courage," he told me,
OL,18,Fin an interview for ITV's Tonight
OL,19,Fprogramme.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+.!/*%/"-$ /*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,
