OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F312A1707500434
OL,3,CFormer Tory leader warns of
OL,4,Cexistential threat if party fails to
OL,5,Cpull together
OL,7,F"And we've seen that already in his
OL,8,Fpremiership. How capable he is of
OL,9,Fdoing that, of keeping going. I think
OL,10,Fit was meant to be Winston Churchill
OL,11,Fwho said, 'if you are in hell, keep
OL,12,Fgoing'. That's the only way out. Don't
OL,13,Fstand still."
OL,15,FLord Hague, who has been somewhat of a
OL,16,Fmentor to Mr Sunak since the younger
OL,17,Fpolitician took over as MP for
OL,18,FRichmond, in Yorkshire, said he was an
OL,19,Fexcellent prime minister, who was
OL,20,Fhardworking, focused on detail, honest
OL,21,Fand had high standards.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/15
