OL,3,CFormer Tory leader warns of
OL,4,Cexistential threat if party fails to
OL,5,Cpull together
OL,7,F"It's a big shock to be a party
OL,8,Fleader. Suddenly you're responsible
OL,9,Ffor everybody and everything in the
OL,10,Fparty. And that requires being really
OL,11,Fgood at party politics... (of)
OL,12,Fthinking of things in a very partisan
OL,13,Fway, in a very party political way.
OL,14,FAnd that comes harder to Rishi...
OL,16,F"Anybody would find it tough. But I
OL,17,Fthink for, for such a, such an
OL,18,Fintelligent and rational person, the
OL,19,Foperation of party politics is a bit
OL,20,Fharder."
