OL,3,CFormer Tory leader warns of
OL,4,Cexistential threat if party fails to
OL,5,Cpull together
OL,7,FLord Hague argued that what Mr Sunak
OL,8,Finherited made things extremely
OL,9,Fdifficult, saying it was "like taking
OL,10,Fover an army on the battlefield when
OL,11,Fit's just been fighting himself...
OL,12,FImagine how difficult it is to
OL,13,Fstraighten out that arm and make sure
OL,14,Fit marches in the same direction".
OL,16,FHe argued that no Conservative PM
OL,17,Fwould be in a better position after
OL,18,Finheriting "that battlefield" but
OL,19,Fadmitted things were incredibly
OL,20,Fdifficult for Mr Sunak right now.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/15
