OL,3,CFormer Tory leader warns of
OL,4,Cexistential threat if party fails to
OL,5,Cpull together
OL,7,F'I would say your only chance is to
OL,8,Fwork together,' William Hague tells
OL,9,FAnushka Asthana when she asked about
OL,10,Fdisloyal MPs
OL,12,FAsked what his message was to disloyal
OL,13,FMPs, Lord Hague said: "I would say
OL,14,Fyour only chance is to work together."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/15
