OL,3,CFormer Tory leader warns of
OL,4,Cexistential threat if party fails to
OL,5,Cpull together
OL,7,FHow long could the pain go on for the
OL,8,FConservatives, I asked. "If a party
OL,9,Fgoes into opposition, there's no
OL,10,Fguarantee of when it will get back or
OL,11,Fif it will ever get back. When the
OL,12,FLiberals went into opposition in the
OL,13,F1920s, they never came back other than
OL,14,Fas a coalition partner every 30 years
OL,15,For so. There's no guarantee of ever
OL,16,Fcoming back."
OL,18,FHave you heard our new podcast Talking
OL,19,FPolitics? Every week Tom, Robert and
OL,20,FAnushka dig into the biggest issues
OL,21,Fdominating the political agenda...
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/15
