OL,7,FHe urged MPs to see this election year
OL,8,Fas being in the "sales department".
OL,10,F"You're not in the creativity
OL,11,Fdepartment anymore. You're not in the
OL,12,Fredesign department, you are in the
OL,13,Fsales department.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/15
