OL,3,CFormer Tory leader warns of
OL,4,Cexistential threat if party fails to
OL,5,Cpull together
OL,7,F"Conservative MPs need to understand
OL,8,Fthat they've actually got a better
OL,9,Fstory to tell than some of them
OL,10,Fsometimes give the impression and
OL,11,Fthey've got a really good Prime
OL,12,FMinister, and they really ought to be
OL,13,Fable to sell that. But they all do
OL,14,Fhave to join in selling it.
OL,16,FHe said he hoped Mr Sunak and the
OL,17,Fparty would at least make the election
OL,18,Fcompetitive, arguing that however much
OL,19,Fit looked like the Tories would lose,
OL,20,Fit wasn't a done deal.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G10/15
