OL,3,CFormer Tory leader warns of
OL,4,Cexistential threat if party fails to
OL,5,Cpull together
OL,7,F"It might turn out that that's just
OL,8,Ftoo difficult, that the accumulation
OL,9,Fof years in office and all the
OL,10,Fproblems the country and the world has
OL,11,Fexperienced in that time will prove
OL,12,Ftoo much. That might be true, but it's
OL,13,Fnot definitely true. It's not written
OL,14,Fin stone or in the stars. We still
OL,15,Fhave a choice at the next election."
OL,17,FHe argued that the Tories were in a
OL,18,Fbetter position than when he was
OL,19,Fleader between 1997 and 2001.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G11/15
