OL,7,FLord Hague described how he was
OL,8,Fimpressed by Mr Sunak from the moment
OL,9,Fhe saw him on stage at a selection for
OL,10,Fthe Richmond seat that he had
OL,11,Fpreviously held. He said he knew
OL,12,Fimmediately that Mr Sunak would go far.
OL,14,FI asked about Mr Sunak's somewhat
OL,15,F"eager" nature that I saw while we
OL,16,Fwere filming for the Tonight
OL,17,Fprogramme. Almost "Tigger-like" I said.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G12/15
