OL,7,FLord Hague replied: "There's something
OL,8,Fmuch more sophisticated and powerful
OL,9,Fhere than Tigger. But nevertheless, I
OL,10,Fknow what you mean by eager."
OL,12,FHe described Mr Sunak getting up at
OL,13,F5am to go cow-milking with farmers as
OL,14,Fa candidate, and still working at 10
OL,15,Fat night in the Cabinet room as PM -
OL,16,Fgoing through papers.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G13/15
